item.title: CVE-2022-4384|2024-08-03T01:41:44.451Z -- unknown -- stream
item.description: The Stream WordPress plugin before 3.9.2 does not prevent users with little privileges on the site (like subscribers) from using its alert creation functionality, which may enable them to leak sensitive information.
